        <%- include('_header') %>
        <div class="container text-white text-center bg-dark" style="border-radius: 1em;">
            <br>
            <h1 style="font-weight: 700;">Endpoints</h1>
            <p>Below you can view the added endpoints we support at this time.</p>
            <br>
            <div class="container">
                <ul class="text-start">
                    <li>
                        <p><span style="font-weight: 700;">GET:</span> <code>/api/checkuser/:userId</code></p>
                        <p>This will return an array of all bans from a userId. Allowing you to properly check if the userId is banned or not!</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><span style="font-weight: 700;">POST:</span> <code>/api/postban</code></p>
                        <p>This endpoint allows you to post your bans inside of the firewallgg ban notified Discord channel for members and followers to see.</p>
                        <ul class="text-start">
                            <li>
                                <p><code>userId</code> | <span style="font-weight: 800;">STRING</span> | The userId of the user you have banned.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p><code>userTag</code> | <span style="font-weight: 800;">STRING</span> | The tag of the user you have banned (Wumpus#0001).</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p><code>databaseName</code> | <span style="font-weight: 800;">STRING</span> | The name of your ban database.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p><code>banReason</code> | <span style="font-weight: 800;">STRING</span> | The reason you have decided to ban this user.</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p><code>banProof</code> | <span style="font-weight: 800;">STRING</span> | An <em>IMAGE LINK</em> provided as evidence to backup the reason.</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
